Third-party data vendored in this repository (refs/ocp/):

- graphite_LGM50_ocp_Chen2020.csv, nmc_LGM50_ocp_Chen2020.csv,
  nca_ocp_Kim2011_data.csv, graphite_ocp_Ecker2015.csv — from PyBaMM
  (github.com/pybamm-team/PyBaMM), BSD 3-Clause License. Original sources:
  Chen et al. 2020 J. Electrochem. Soc. 167 080534; Kim et al. 2011;
  Ecker et al. 2015.
- Kokam_OCV_NMC.csv, Kokam_OCV_C.csv — from SLIDE
  (github.com/Battery-Intelligence-Lab/SLIDE), BSD 3-Clause License,
  Copyright (c) 2019 The Chancellor, Masters and Scholars of the University
  of Oxford.

Datasets used (not redistributed here; download instructions in README):
- Severson et al. 2019, Nature Energy (data.matr.io)
- Preger et al. 2020, J. Electrochem. Soc. (BatteryArchive / BatteryLife
  mirror; double-attribution license)
- Birkl & Howey 2017, Oxford Battery Degradation Dataset 1
  (doi:10.5287/bodleian:KO2kdmYGg)
